(211, 'Scale Barding', 'G', 'Barding is armor designed to protect an animal\'s head, neck, chest, and body. \n\n	Scale barding provides a mount with an AC equal to 14 + the mount\'s Dexterity modifier (max 2). The mount makes Dexterity (Stealth) checks with disadvantage. \n\n \n\nSource: Player\'s Handbook, p. 157', '', '', '90', '', '', '', '', '', '200', '', '', '', ''),
(212, 'Scholar\'s Pack', 'G', 'Includes: \n\n	â€¢ a backpack \n\n	â€¢ a book of lore \n\n	â€¢ a bottle of ink \n\n	â€¢ an ink pen \n\n	â€¢ 10 sheets of parchment \n\n	â€¢ a little bag of sand \n\n	â€¢ a small knife. \n\n \n\nSource: Player\'s Handbook p. 151', '', '', '10', '', '', '', '', '', '40', '', '', '', ''),
