(807, 'Mithral Breastplate', 'MA', 'Mithral is a light, flexible metal. A mithral chain shirt or breastplate can be worn under normal clothes. If the armor normally imposes disadvantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks or has a Strength requirement, the mithral version of the armor doesn\'t. \n\n \n\nSource: Dungeon Master\'s Guide p. 182', '1', 'uncommon', '20', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '14', '', ''),
