id of magic or a special sense. For the purpose of hiding, the creature is heavily obscured. The creature\'s location can be detected by any noise it makes or any tracks it leaves. \n\n \n\nâ€¢ Attack rolls against the creature have disadvantage, and the creature\'s attack rolls have advantage.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
